premise_source_doc_sentence: Following a series of French albums during the 1980s , she signed on to Epic Records in the United States .
Her recordings are mainly in French and English , although she also sings in Spanish , Italian , German , Latin , Japanese , and Mandarin Chinese .
Céline Dion chante Noël  (  meaning Céline Dion Sings Christmas  )  is a French-language Christmas album by Canadian singer Celine Dion , released in Quebec , Canada on 4 December 1981 .
